                                        <p>Universis ad quos presentes littere pervenerint, frater <persName key="d1e12750" xml:id="d1e134660">A. dictus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282500" xml:id="d1e134662" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Cîteaux">Cistercii</orgName>
                        </persName> salutem <lb n="2" /> in summo salutari. Cum sepe fratres nostri
                        de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284222" xml:id="d1e134667" corresp="abbaye de la Ferté-sur-Grosne (1113 -)">Firmitate</orgName>
                        diuturnam exposu<lb n="3" break="no" />issent querimoniam de fratribus
                        nostris <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e134672" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>, capitulo generali super quinde<lb n="4" break="no" />cim jugeribus terre que fratres de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e134678" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneto</orgName> apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324406" xml:id="d1e134681" corresp="Beaune (Côte-d'Or)">Belnam</placeName> injuste
                        occupare <lb n="5" /> dicebant cum sibi competerent de elemosina <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324624" xml:id="d1e134686" corresp="Eudes III, duc de Bourgogne (1192-1218)">O. nobilis ducis <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325098" xml:id="d1e134688" corresp="Bourgogne">Burgundie</placeName>
                        </persName>, <lb n="6" /> nos tandem de voluntate capituli generalis <add place="above" hand="eademmanu">eandem querelam</add> suscepimus
                        terminandam. Partibus <lb n="7" /> itaque apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324406" xml:id="d1e134699" corresp="Beaune (Côte-d'Or)">Belnam</placeName> convocatis et
                        rei veritate tam per ducem quam per alios diligen<lb n="8" break="no" />tissime inquisita et inventa, de consensu parcium et nostro assensu,
                        fratribus <lb n="9" /> nostris de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284222" xml:id="d1e134706" corresp="abbaye de la Ferté-sur-Grosne (1113 -)">Firmitate</orgName> dederunt quinquaginta libras
                        fratres de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e134710" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneto</orgName> et illi <lb n="10" /> querelam hanc in perpetuum
                        quitaverunt. In hujus rei memoriam presentem car<lb n="11" break="no" />tam
                        sigillo nostro fecimus consignari. Actum anno gratie <num>m° cc°
                        xii°</num>.</p>
                
